- Development and demo will run on a personal laptop/desktop with a webcam (no dedicated industrial hardware).
- A single GPU (or CPU-only, with realistic FPS expectations) is available for training and inference.
- The evaluator/guide is fine with a locally-run demo (Docker Compose) rather than a live cloud deployment, though optional deployment is a bonus.

